"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"[https://wrongalot.substack.com/p/simple-and-short-guide-not-only-for](https://wrongalot.substack.com/p/simple-and-short-guide-not-only-for)\\n\\n纯粹学习，非投资建议\\n\\n其实作为我一个2017年入场的老韭菜，行业发展之快，让我应接不暇，让我变得在2021年年末和2017年年底一样成为一个Noobs（心态彻底归零，重来吧）\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/mattigags/status/1463430142081093641](https://twitter.com/mattigags/status/1463430142081093641)\\n\\n**a lesson #1 in crypto: Be skeptical of any advice.**\\n\\n\\\\*\\\\*其实就是DYOR的思想（\\\\*\\\\*Do Your Own Research）\\n\\n1、生存第一，不要破产\\n\\n[https://www.paradigm.xyz/2021/03/surviving-crypto-cycles/](https://www.paradigm.xyz/2021/03/surviving-crypto-cycles/)\\n\\n# Surviving Crypto Cycles\\n\\n[Surviving Crypto Cycles](https://www.paradigm.xyz/2021/03/surviving-crypto-cycles/)\\n\\n我是一个经历牛熊周期的韭菜了，在上一个周期我目标就是生存下来，熬过漫长的熊市。\\n\\n遵守牛市赚钱、熊市赚币的原则\\n\\nCuriosity is the best predictor of longevity in this space. If you’re curious - you’re likely on a path to transform the speculator in you into a builder or a power user. But sometimes you have to follow more cues than just the price.\\n\\n保持好奇心，在上一个周期，这方面我做得非常不成功，我基本上固守在比特币的叙事里面，连Eth公链这块都没太多的去涉猎，而对币安、CZ等的偏见，让我错失了太多机会。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/BOidYDrOSsB6pNbF1PCmD.jpeg?height=720&width=960)\\n\\n在推特上关注各种kol，每天update新信息现在成了我的生活，然后把学习的内容整理到mirror上面，这个月我发现了Mirror的作用，深深的爱上了Mirror.\\n\\n[https://hive.one/explore](https://hive.one/explore)\\n\\n这里有可以关注的KOL\\n\\n### CT Disclaimers\\n\\nThe true alpha gets synthesized in your mind from bits and pieces of Twitter, governance forums and private conversations.\\n\\n真正好的机会需要学习整理，从twitter、medium、Reddit、Mirror等点点滴滴合成到你的头脑中。\\n\\n### TG 和 Discord\\n\\n这两个我都用得还不是很熟悉，特别爽Discord\\n\\n**Discord 社区的例子有[Alchemist](http://discord.alchemist.wtf/)、[OlympusDAO](https://discord.com/invite/olympusdao)**、**[KlimaDAO](http://discord.gg/KlimaDAO)**、**[Forgotten Runes](https://discord.com/invite/forgottenrunes)**和**[Abacus](https://discord.com/invite/TX2Te3X8UJ)**。\\n\\n### 降低期望\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fzGAnkYRwWy-wfcyeLD_v.jpeg?height=235&width=957)\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/zhusu/status/1471731995159908355?s=20](https://twitter.com/zhusu/status/1471731995159908355?s=20)\\n\\nCrypto is filled w examples of learning the wrong lessons from history 2013-2015, seeing alts fail, then writing off coins like eth more broadly 2018-2020, seeing eos fail, then writing off coins like avax, sol more broadly Funds who held down 90% in 2018, sold early in 2020\\n\\n从失败中寻求机会\\n\\nThe mkt has gone from Bitcoin to blockchain not Bitcoin to Bitcoin not blockchain to now Bitcoin and blockchain\\n\\nYour success in crypto probably depends on your ability to *“to follow your curiosity”*.\\n\\n保持好奇心\",\"timestamp\":1640343598,\"title\":\"简单的加密新手指南\"},\"digest\":\"-sbOSWlc3OYo9t9H-ZRY1DAE3O3HKUjgKw7icf4mnuw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xd8E93E06a84581c10DC1F9F60ec91f0F38994f1b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cMFgJWo0R83IUGP-oC59cCKhgfKZrezq-aV3fQc1AbU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"86rM09yJV_iikmgyczrUUMM5VZnQukEhY2ZNhB6MoeM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"_DsYLZ4Jeh6HI_p7rQmjjxlo15MFbLtXq0ywJ6KVS44oA2LH2HTs3BgRg1O8d41m5cJ1OAcJzb9xlwc6I6ikdg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x55561c7f900b4987fad58cdc00d1050605ccc32081b4ec5049f35b5f327004393564d889a3c6c359c17cf0f2e7910adf9841dd8da6452b86f800d0eb1a62cd481b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cMFgJWo0R83IUGP-oC59cCKhgfKZrezq-aV3fQc1AbU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"86rM09yJV_iikmgyczrUUMM5VZnQukEhY2ZNhB6MoeM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"eFQ48Lq7LBTj04TLiQ-ek0TXcv3q8UwQPRTfDC2FNCw\"}"